            Measurement and Instrumentation Data Center (MIDC)

         Welcome to the Measurement and Instrumentation
         Data Center (MIDC), providing Irradiance and
         Meteorological Data from the following stations: NREL


                 SRRL Baseline Measurement System (BMS)
                            NREL/SRRL, Golden, Colorado

                 SRRL Baseline Surface Radiation Network (BSRN)
                                    NREL/SRRL, Golden, Colorado

                 SRRL Atmospheric Optical Calibration System (AOCS)
                                        NREL/SRRL, Golden, Colorado

                 SRRL Schott Rotating Shadowband Pyranometer (RSP)
                                       NREL/SRRL, Golden, Colorado

                 SRRL Ascension Technology Inc. RSP (ATI)
                              NREL/SRRL, Golden, Colorado

                 National Wind Technology Center M2 Tower
                             NREL/NWTC, Boulder, Colorado

                 South Park Mountain Data (SPMD)
                            South Park, Colorado

                 San Clemente Island Data (SCID)
                        San Clemente, California

                 Bluefield State College (BSC)
                      Bluefield, West Virginia

                 Elizabeth City State University (ECSU)
                         Elizabeth City, North Carolina
